{"tid":2516742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"維基百科用戶：維吾爾族沒有被任何全球組織認定為「種族滅絕」","createTime":"2021-05-05T00:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T21:12:44.000Z","uid":10540,"like":10,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"97efa19e6fe523722e406b658cb74caa65502a0b","tid":2516742,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:32:57.000Z","msg":"請各位於Talk:維吾爾族種族滅絕討論的維基人至此討論。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>目前達成的共識</strong><br />\n沒有被任何全球組織認定為「種族滅絕」。<br />\n所有指控均有合理反駁。（合乎常理、邏輯，而非任何觀點。）<br />\n反對指控的國家比支持的更多。<br />\n以上幾點均支持「該『種族滅絕』未被公認」的觀點。<br />\n將條目命名為「&hellip;&hellip;種族滅絕」會使人誤以為「種族滅絕」是已經被確認的事實。<br />\n「&hellip;&hellip;種族滅絕」和「&hellip;&hellip;指控」是兩個不同的概念。<br />\n條目主要內容不是「種族滅絕」，而是指控、反指控和政治立場。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「維吾爾族種族滅絕」並非指控</strong><br />\n反對方認為「維吾爾族種族滅絕」事實上是有大量可靠的證據所支持的，並非缺乏證據。「維吾爾族種族滅絕」是由具公信力的媒體所報導,以當地的衛星圖變化，當地採訪和已逃亡的當事人為證據<br />\n支持方認為：有更多的國家，以及一些媒體、組織，認為維吾爾族種族滅絕不存在。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">大家可以用讀者身份去表達意見</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:%E4%BA%92%E5%8A%A9%E5%AE%A2%E6%A0%88/%E6%9D%A1%E7%9B%AE%E6%8E%A2%E8%AE%A8#%E2%80%9C%E7%BB%B4%E5%90%BE%E5%B0%94%E6%97%8F%E7%A7%8D%E6%97%8F%E7%81%AD%E7%BB%9D%E2%80%9D%E5%B9%B6%E9%9D%9E%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FWikipedia%3A%25E4%25BA%2592%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%25A0%2588%2F%25E6%259D%25A1%25E7%259B%25AE%25E6%258E%25A2%25E8%25AE%25A8%23%25E2%2580%259C%25E7%25BB%25B4%25E5%2590%25BE%25E5%25B0%2594%25E6%2597%258F%25E7%25A7%258D%25E6%2597%258F%25E7%2581%25AD%25E7%25BB%259D%25E2%2580%259D%25E5%25B9%25B6%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK7np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=011cc168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:%E4%BA%92%E5%8A%A9%E5%AE%A2%E6%A0%88/%E6%9D%A1%E7%9B%AE%E6%8E%A2%E8%AE%A8#%E2%80%9C%E7%BB%B4%E5%90%BE%E5%B0%94%E6%97%8F%E7%A7%8D%E6%97%8F%E7%81%AD%E7%BB%9D%E2%80%9D%E5%B9%B6%E9%9D%9E%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7</a>"},{"pid":"b3fc6956a19fdb5caed4c2ee2f0a99ccf96e57f4","tid":2516742,"uid":49392,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:36:48.000Z","msg":"英國議會同美國政府唔存在"},{"pid":"edc35ef43c83ebb33b870d3834c96571e82728e4","tid":2516742,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:37:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當英國議會同美國政府唔存在</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5aaad1eea277824a21f6b000c2064bfad5557937","tid":2516742,"uid":196924,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:40:20.000Z","msg":"晒氣啦<br />\n中文維基係共黨5毛集中地"},{"pid":"836995c6f2ed2ad16153ed0c86df37e965811102","tid":2516742,"uid":3873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:46:56.000Z","msg":"非洲兄弟嘅作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2309dba782edcb947bdd7ba4d48d290c9e1358ba","tid":2516742,"uid":292987,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:47:46.000Z","msg":"有更多的國家，以及一些媒體、組織<br />\n<br />\n而家鬥人多呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲濕鳩國家用錢買返嚟有咩公信力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cfedebda04e333e4ee97e2b3c8466460993cd7d","tid":2516742,"uid":155095,"like":15,"dislike":7,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"5aaad1eea277824a21f6b000c2064bfad5557937","tid":2516742,"uid":196924,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:40:20.000Z","msg":"晒氣啦<br />\n中文維基係共黨5毛集中地"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:48:08.000Z","msg":"因為香港人唔肯做冇名冇利嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n維基百科先會俾中共五毛黨佔據"},{"pid":"a239febf42edcf694186b8b119ed6b83062aa930","tid":2516742,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a570289c6b5a8714feb3f